security being distributed in the United States, and such activity might result in the harm that Rule 10b&hyph;6 was
designed to prevent (i.e., the creation of artificial prices by persons participating in the distribution).
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=5 f=1 -->
