<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
director (compliance), an industry member shall submit a 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
written report containing information on sponsorships, 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
advertisements, promotions, and other activities pertaining to 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
its business subject to the Act conducted by, or on behalf of, 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
or benefiting the industry member. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(2) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Preparation. 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

