<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
industry member in letter form, executed under the penalties of 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
perjury, and will contain the information specified by the 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
regional director (compliance). 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(3) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Filing. 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
The report will be filed in accordance with 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
the instructions of the regional director (compliance). 
