Par. 23.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 Section 6.82 is removed and reserved. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=4 -->
Par. 24.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 Section 6.83 is revised to read as follows: 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=80 g=1 f=1 -->
&sect;6.83 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=89 g=1 f=1 -->
Product displays. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
(a) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
General.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 The act by an industry member of giving or 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
selling product displays to a retailer does not constitute a 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
means to induce within the meaning of section 105(b)(3) of the 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Act provided that the conditions prescribed in paragraph (c) of 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
this section are met. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(b) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Definition.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 ``Product display'' means any wine racks, 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
bins, barrels, casks, shelving, and similar items the primary 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
function of which is to hold and display consumer products. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(c) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Conditions and limitations.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 (1) The total value of all product displays furnished by an industry member under paragraph (a) of this section may
not exceed $500 per brand at any one time in any one retail 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
establishment. Industry members may not pool or combine 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
dollar limitations in order to provide a retailer a product 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
display valued in excess of $500 per brand. The value of a 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
product display is the actual cost to the industry member who 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
initially purchased it. Transportation and installation costs 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
are excluded. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(2) All product displays must bear conspicuous and 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
substantial advertising matter on the product or the industry 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
member which is permanently inscribed or permanently affixed. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
The name and address of the retailer may appear on the product 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
displays. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(3) The giving or selling of such product displays may be 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
conditioned upon the purchase of the distilled spirits, wine, 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
or malt beverage product advertised on those displays in a 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
quantity necessary for the completion of such display or the 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
use of such materials. No other condition can be imposed by 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
the industry member on the retailer in order for the retailer 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
to receive or obtain the product display. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

