(1) Assure implementation of this part and compliance with its provisions.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(2) Determine whether the provisions of the Soldiers' and Sailors' Civil Relief Act (SSCRA) have been complied with
under the provisions of Public Law 103&hyph;94.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(3) Act as the DoD Executive Agent for forms prescribed by this part, or otherwise necessary to process involuntary
allotments.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(e) The 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

