<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(2) That the member has 15 calendar days from the date of receipt of the notice to respond to the commander by completing
Part II of DD Form bb and submitting any information or documentation deemed relevant by the member. That for good cause
