</FOOTNAME>
<!-- PJG ITAG l=28 g=1 f=1 -->
EPA is not finding that it is legally obligated to use rulemaking procedures to approve the OTC recommendation. EPA
reserves the right to approve future OTC recommendations without following rulemaking procedures.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->
</FOOTNOTE>

<FOOTNOTE>
<FOOTNAME>
<!-- PJG ITAG l=28 g=1 f=1 -->
4
