the OTC recommendation. The Agency is not legally obligating itself to follow rulemaking procedures to the extent
it disapproves or partially disapproves the OTC recommendation, although the Agency currently intends to follow
the procedures set forth in 307(d) regardless of whether it approves or disapproves the OTC recommendation.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

