<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(5) Rule 12&hyph;07_Accumulated Depreciation, Depletion and Amortization of Property, Plant and Equipment. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(6) 12&hyph;08_Guarantees of Securities of Other Issuers. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
