of the 1992 Act; paragraph (b)(4) is added to address the need for periodic meetings; and paragraph (b)(5) is revised
to clarify when SCSEP funds can be used for enrollee transportation.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
