the goal for unsubsidized placement has not been achieved.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
15. Section 641.315 is revised to permit restricted limits on the duration of enrollment.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
